'''blob'''
#A shapeless or [[amorphous]] mass; a [[vague]] [[shape]] or [[amount]], especially of a liquid or semisolid substance; a [[clump]], [[group]], [[collection]] or [[cluster]] lacking a definite shape.
#:''She judged by the '''blob''' of toothpaste in the sink that her toddler had figured out how to unscrew caps.''

